All Implemented Interfaces:
com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.Nameable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.Named, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.StringSource
public class CsvColumn<Type> extends com.telenav.kivakit.core.value.name.Name
A typesafe model of a CSV column that belongs to a CsvSchema and can convert values for the column between strings and objects.

CsvColumns are added to a CsvSchema with CsvSchema(CsvColumn[]) and then used as a key to retrieve values from CsvLine. This model includes the CSV schema that owns it, as well as the name and index of the column in the data. A StringConverter converts values for the column to and from objects.

Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
